Package com.samsung.fastcast.msgs

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CustomEvent
    CustomEvent class is base class for events that can be created outside library by programmer implementing his scenario.
    ErrorMessage
    Error message to transport error code and human readable message
    KeydownMessage
    Keydown message to transport information about keys.
    MessageBase
    Base class for all messages exchanged between mobile and TV.
    PlayMessage
    Play message to transport information about start new movie.
    SeekMessage
    Seek message to transport seek command
    SimpleTextMessage
    Simple text message class.
    StatusMessage
    StatusMessage class to transport information about remote player status
    VolumeMessage
    Volume message class to transport information about volume level change
  • Enum Summary
